{
  "stem": "4760.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "These people found that stone and wrote a beautiful note to my friends that they-- that we are still alive and that we are on the transport.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They don't know where, but least they know that we are still living.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, any-- anybody-- I mean, not everybody does that-- just find the note, and to-- to notify that-- that you are still alive.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then, we were put in, and again, in boxcars on a train of about-- I would say, they transported that time 1,500 people to Germany at a time.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how many people were in that camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And were-- what were conditions like in that train?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On that train?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Was it-- was it different from the first one that--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no difference.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a little straw on the floor where we could sit down.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And can you imagine having 60 peoples in a boxcar?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A boxcar is the size of this room, a little larger, and having people sitting there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the middle, they had a big drum where you have to go and urinate, or if you have to do something else.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, at night, they would dump it someplace.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you would step over people, in order to get to the boxcar.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They would give you a piece of bread like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and they would have a bucket of water in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And everybody drank out of the bucket of water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we arrived at Buchenwald, after two and a half days, almost three days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In Buchenwald, naturally, we were taken from the station and bussed-- not on buses-- on-- on trucks into the Camp Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there, we were again stripped from head to toe, shaven from head-- all over, from head to toe, shaven.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
